  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.4">
<l>uṭaṉamar kātaṉ makaḷir tirumakaṇ maṇmaka ḷāyar</l>
<l>maṭamaka ḷeṉṟivar mūva rāḷu mulakamu mūṉṟē</l>
<l>yuṭaṉavai yokka viḻuṅki yālilaic cērntava ṉemmāṉ</l>
<l>kaṭaṉmali māyap perumāṉ kaṇṇaṉe ṉokkalai yāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who rules over the beloved woman with whom together he resides, these three,</l>
<l>namely lady Śrī, lady Earth and an youthful daughter if the cowherds, who joined</l>
<l>a Banyan leaf after having swallowed all the three worlds, so as to be harmoniously together,</l>
<l>our lord, the great lord of ample Māyā on the sea, Kṛṣṇa is part of my body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
